Well this has had to be the most boring summer ive been through, at least last year i had friends i lived near so i could hang out. I know, i know, shut the fuck up duffy no one cares! I really feel like i could just disappear, and when school started again no one would notice I'm gone. I guess that kind of explains why i haven't been on AIM all summer, not like i talked to anyone before that. I wish my family had moved to florida like they have been saying, even more so after i admitted that i really wanted to. I guess it would be like a new start for me, ya know? Hell if anyone reads this it will be the first time someone outside of family has heard from me, unless you count that weird bulletin i sent out last week. I think that sophomore year changed me, wait, i know it did, but I'm trying to figure out if it was for the better or not. I'll admit my self esteem went up a little, but i started hanging out with other people less and less, and some of the people i did hang out with i really didnt like too much.

Also all my pillows are almost the same age as i am, ._. i finally am realizing just how much flat pillows fuck up your neck = lack of sleep = more thinking at night = tired cranky Duff = this LJ post.
